Detailed Description

RNAStructML -- XML representation of rna secondary structures, uses dotBracket

Namespace: http://hobit.sourceforge.net/xsds/20060201/rnastructML.xsd Homepage: http://hobit.sourceforge.net/xsds/20060201/rnastructML.xsd

Author:
Kai Loewenthal <kloewent@techfak.uni-bielefeld.de> Jan Krüger <jkrueger@techfak.uni-bielefeld.de>
Version:
1.0 TODO : Current version does not support crossrefs!
Exceptions:
BioDOMException on failure / fatal error
